<title>Open a Sort Specification or Dictionary File</title>
<context HID_FILE_OPEN />

<list ordered>
	<li>Click <image open_button.png /> on the toolbar; or from the <b>File</b> menu, select <b>Open</b>; or press <b>Ctrl+O</b>.</li>
	<li>Select the sort specification file (*.ssf) or dictionary file (*.dcf) you want to open.</li>
</list>

See <link save_a_sort_specification_file.hgt>save a sort specification file</link> on how to create it. If you have never created a sort specification file, you must open the dictionary file which describes the data you want to sort.
